          Comparison of the subcellular localization signals
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">uncovers</ENAMEX> clear distinctions between <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">AtCOP1 and MmCOP1</TIMEX>. In
          AtCOP1, the sequence responsible for the cytoplasmic
