          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">NES</ENAMEX> within the corresponding <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">region</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">Fig 8</ENAMEX>), even though
          we have not eliminated the possible involvement of other
