          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">NLS</ENAMEX> variant, which is composed of <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">96</NUMEX> amino <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">acids</ENAMEX>
