          in the intermediate region of coiled-coil domain and the
          WD-40 domain [ [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">17</TIMEX> ] ; <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Fig 8</ENAMEX>]. Interestingly in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">MmCOP1</TIMEX>,
          the site matching the <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">AtCOP1</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">NLS</ENAMEX> is found to be important
